'''''Star Wars Insider'' 91''' is the 91st issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'', released in [[November]] [[2006]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*"Letter from the Editor"
*"[[Comlink (department)|Comlink]]"
*"[[Skywalking]]"
**"[[George Lucas|Lucas]] Talks ''Star Wars'' TV"
**"[[Refresher Reading]]: 20 Things You Don't Know About the [[Mos Eisley/Legends|Mos Eisley]] [[Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina/Legends|Cantina]]" {{C|by [[Pablo Hidalgo]]}}
**"Expanded Universe, Meet the Paparazzi" {{C|by [[Chenda Ngak]]}}
*"[[Jedi Library (department)|Jedi Library]]" &mdash; Questions of [[Allegiance (novel)|''Allegiance'']] {{C|by [[Jason Fry]]}}
*"[[Drawn by the Force]]" &mdash; [[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic: Days of Fear|Don't Tell Yoda]] {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]]}}
*"[[Jabba's Collection]]" &mdash; Heavy Metal
*"[[Set Piece|Technical Readout]]" &mdash; X-wing Starfighter {{C|by [[Chris Trevas]]}}
*"[[Ask Lobot|Ask the Master]]" &mdash; What Ever Happened to [[HoloNet News/Legends|HoloNet News]]?" {{C|by Pablo Hidalgo}}
*"[[Scouting the Galaxy]]" &mdash; Where's the ''Star Wars'' Stuff? Everywhere! {{C|by [[Stephen J. Sansweet|Steve Sansweet]]}}
*"[[International Collecting|Star Wars International]]" &mdash; Tokyo Treasures" {{C|by [[Gus Lopez]]}}
*"[[Best of Hyperspace]]" {{C|by [[Bonnie Burton]] and Pablo Hidalgo}}
*"[[Padawan's Corner|Padawan Corner]]" &mdash; DIY R2-D2 Pinhole Camera" {{C|by Bonnie Burton}}
*[[Bantha Tracks (department)|''Bantha Tracks'']] Vol. 22 {{C|by [[Mary Franklin]]}}

===Features===
*"[[The Man Behind the Mask (Star Wars Insider 91)|The Man Behind the Mask]]" {{C|by [[Cesar G. Soriano]]}}
*:<small>Actor [[David Prowse]] talks about 30 years as cinema's most iconic villain, Darth Vader.</small>
*"[[Guilty By Association: Early Star Wars Bootleg Merchandise|Guilty By Association: Early ''Star Wars'' Bootleg Merchandise]]" {{C|by [[Pete Vilmur]]}}
*:<small>Bootleg lightsabers, unlicensed posters, fan magazines and artwork&mdash;''Star Wars'' has a rich legacy of underground goods. ''Insider'' is proud to present a history lesson you don't want to miss.</small>
*"[[Pirates of the Boards]]" Part 1 of 6" {{C|by [[Jonathan W. Rinzler|J. W. Rinzler]]}}
*:<small>The first of a six-part series featuring [[Joe Johnston]]'s never-before-seen storyboards from an early draft of the original ''Star Wars''.</small>
*"[[The Models of Revenge of the Sith|Hell Raising: The Models of ''Revenge of the Sith'', Part II]]" {{C|by [[Frank Parisi]]}}
*:<small>In the second of a three-part series, [[Brian Gernand]], head of ILM's model shop for Episodes II and III, details how he and his team created the Purgatory of a galaxy far, far away: Mustafar.</small>
*"[[Comic Marvels]]" {{C|by [[Jason Fry]]}}
*:<small>From quixotic Jedi to telepathic bunnies we take an in-depth look at the best, worst, and the strangest from the Marvel Comics ''Star Wars'' series.</small>

